\c 5
\p
\v 1 Saizvozvo mabasa ose akaitirwa imba yaJehovha naSoromoni akapera. Zvino Soromoni akapinza zvinhu zvakange zvatsaurirwa Jehovha nababa vake Dhavhidhi, sirivha, nendarama, nenhumbi dzose, akadziisa muzvivigiro zveimba yaMwari.
\s Temberi inotsaurirwa Jehovha
\p
\v 2 Zvino Soromoni akaunganidza vakuru valsiraeri, navakuru vose vamarudzi, iwo machinda edzimba dzamadzibaba avana vaIsraeri, paJerusarema, akakwidza areka yesungano yaJehovha ibve paguta raDhavhidhi, iro Ziyoni.
\v 3 Varume vose vaIsraeri vakaungana kuna mambo pamutambo, wakange uri pamwedzi wechinomwe.
\v 4 Vakuru vose vaIsraeri vakasvika, vaRevhi vakasimudza areka.
\p
\v 5 Vakakwira neareka, netende rokusangana, nenhumbi dzose tsvene dzakange dziri muTende; vapristi vaRevhi vakakwira naizvozvo.
\v 6 Mambo Soromoni, neungano yose yavaIsraeri yakange yaunganira kwaari, vakafamba pamberi peareka, vakabayira makwai nenzombe, zvakange zvisingagoni kuverengwa nokuwanda kwazvo.
\v 7 Ipapo vapristi vakagadzika areka yesungano yaJehovha panzvimbo yayo, panzvimbo tsvene yeimba, panzvimbo tsvene-tsvene, ipo panyasi pamapapiro amakerubhi.
\v 8 Nokuti makerubhi akatambanudza mapapiro awo pamusoro penzvimbo yeareka, makerubhi akafukidza areka namatanda ayo nechokumusoro.
\v 9 Matanda akange akareba; naizvozvo miromo yamatanda yakange ichionekwa kana munhu ari paareka pamberi penzvimbo tsvene; asi akange asingaonekwi nechokunze, ichipo kusvikira nhasi.
\v 10 Mukati meareka makange musisine chiro, asi mabwendefa maviri akange aiswamo naMozisi paHorebhu, nguva Jehovha yaakaita sungano navana valsiraeri pakubuda kwavo paEgipita.
\p
\v 11 Zvino vapristi vakati vabuda panzvimbo tsvene (nokuti vapristi vose, vakange varipo, vakange vazvinatsa, vasingaiti hanya namapoka avo;
\v 12 navaRevhi vosewo, vaiva vaimbi, vose vavo, vaiti, Asafi, naHemani, naJedhutuni, nokuvanakomana vavo, navananin'ina vavo, vakafuka micheka michena yakapfava, vanamakandira, nemitengerangwa, nembira, vakamira kurutivi rwamabvazuva rwearitari, uye pamwechete navo vapristi vane zana namakumi maviri, vachiridza hwamanda;)
\v 13 zvino varidzi vehwamanda, navaimbi, vakati vachiita mawa, vachiita nenzwi rimwe vachirumbidza nokuvonga Jehovha; vakati vachiimbisa pamwechete nehwamanda, namakandira, nezvokuridzisa nazvo, vachirumbidza Jehovha, vachiti, nokuti akanaka. Nokuti nyasha dzake dzinogara nokusingaperi; ipapo imba yakazara negore, iyo imba yaJehovha;
\v 14 naizvozvo vapristi vakange vasingagoni kumira pabasa nokuda kwegore; nokuti kubwinya kwaJehovha kwakazadza imba yaMwari.
